12
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:26,400
Hello? Hello?

13
00:04:27,400 --> 00:04:29,800
Oh, why are there so many eyes on me?

14
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:32,800
Hello? Hello?

15
00:04:33,100 --> 00:04:34,800
They're not saying anything.

16
00:04:35,400 --> 00:04:37,400
Oh, I have to get back!

17
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,800
Today is such an important day,

18
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,600
I can't get stuck in here!

19
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:42,500
What should I do?

20
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:47,000
I guess I have to figure this out on my own.

21
00:04:47,400 --> 00:04:50,800
Um... There's so many people looking at me...

22
00:04:50,800 --> 00:04:52,500
Are those Pebbles? Hello!

23
00:04:52,600 --> 00:04:54,600
Are you expecting me to do something?

24
00:04:55,200 --> 00:04:57,200
Maybe I should sing and dance,

25
00:04:57,200 --> 00:04:59,000
'cause this looks like a stage.

26
00:04:59,200 --> 00:05:00,000
Maybe...

27
00:05:00,130 --> 00:05:00,875
Wait, is that how I get out?

28
00:05:00,875 --> 00:05:02,353
Okay... Okay, I got it then!

29
00:05:02,353 --> 00:05:05,420
I'm gonna sing and dance a song right now!

30
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:06,508
Here we go!

31
00:05:06,508 --> 00:05:08,508
This game!

32
00:05:59,141 --> 00:06:04,941
まわり続ける 歯車にはなり下がらない
I won't settle for being a gear that just keeps spinning

33
00:06:05,141 --> 00:06:10,941
平均演じる 誕生から始まった地獄
Playing it safe, a hell that started from birth

34
00:06:11,741 --> 00:06:16,841
遊び半分で 神が導いた 盤上の世界
A game for fun, a board-game world guided by gods

35
00:06:16,841 --> 00:06:17,641
No no no game no life

36
00:06:17,641 --> 00:06:21,041
ぬるい平穏を ばっさり切り捨てて
Cutting away this lukewarm peace

37
00:06:21,041 --> 00:06:25,841
栄光の階段に 存在刻むんだ
Carving my existence into the stairs of glory

38
00:06:26,841 --> 00:06:30,341
目に映るのは 完全勝利の運命
What I see is the fate of complete victory

39
00:06:30,841 --> 00:06:34,641
何もかも 計算通り 変えてやる
I'll change everything exactly as planned

40
00:06:34,641 --> 00:06:39,141
止まらない空白で
With an unstoppable blank space

41
00:06:39,741 --> 00:06:41,641
We are Maverick

42
00:06:41,641 --> 00:06:44,741
救済なんていらない
I don't need any salvation

43
00:06:44,741 --> 00:06:48,841
どんな理不尽も 覆せばいいだけ
I just have to overturn any absurdity

44
00:06:48,841 --> 00:06:52,241
の話
That's all there is to it

45
00:06:52,241 --> 00:06:54,441
才能の駆け引きと
A strategic battle of wits

46
00:06:54,441 --> 00:06:58,241
才能が 無敗誘う
And talent invites invincibility

47
00:06:59,241 --> 00:07:04,641
生まれ落ちた日の手で 楽しむんだ
I'll enjoy it with the hands I was born with

48
00:07:05,641 --> 00:07:11,541
自分だけを 自分 信じてる
I believe in myself, only myself

49
00:07:16,141 --> 00:07:19,841
底に潜む 闇より強い相手はいない
