56
00:07:47,341 --> 00:07:51,241
戦うことは きっと間違いじゃない
Fighting is surely not a mistake

57
00:07:51,241 --> 00:07:55,241
手応えが 教えてくれた
The feeling of it told me so

58
00:07:55,241 --> 00:08:00,241
全て失っても 勝ち残れ
Even if I lose everything, I will survive

59
00:08:00,541 --> 00:08:03,441
We are Maverick

60
